well guys i am starting to update more often (at least i am tryin)lol i guess since i come to my aunt's more and since her computer is faster then i will just update from here..lol well i am starting to get ready for friday..can't wait.lol it will be so much fun..i hope everyone comes..but ne who life is good i guess...friday will be 7months for me and justin...i am so happy..i bet he is too..lol i know he is! who wouldn't be happy to be with me for so long...lols j/k well that is about it for now...i will update later peace gn@

well we will start with yesturday (wed) raye called and invited me over for the day and to spend the night. mom said ok and i came over. then kris called and invited me and raye for ice cream. we went with her then she droped us off. came back to raye's and just chilled online and stuff like that. justin called and he missed 4 questions on his permit test and you are only allowed to miss 3 so *cries* for justin. raye and i talked online for a long time. we finally went downstairs but first we watched a movie before we went to sleep (Men in black 2) awesome movie..lol after it was over we went to sleep. today (thurs) we woke up raye made pancakes which the first two turned out crappy but i ate them ne ways..then raye ate hers and we watched spongebob... came back upstairs...took my showwer now raye is takin hers..we will be gettin ready to leave for kris's house here soon she is coming for us around 2 so this day should be alot of fun....lol can't wait well i will update later if i don't before the 4th....happy 4th of july to everyone who reads....luv ya all peace gn@

it has really been a while guys...i am really sorrie that i haven't been writing but i just haven't been online. Well school is out now and i am so glad summer is here. I love the SUN! Me and Bush are still goin together ( 6 months and counting) i am so happy that he is my b/f. lol and if anyone knew about Colby Cole...he died Thrusday June 12th... So please take a moment and pray for his family and friends who will miss him dearly. *~ Colby James Cole Feb. 14, 1998 - June 12, 2003  age 5 ~* I hope that everyone's summer is goin great and i will try and keep in touch with everyone and if not contact me. lol....miss and luv ya all. peace
gn@
p.s. update a little later

another stinky monday...lol. 1st period i had a test 2nd i had a test 3rd didn't do ne thing we just sat there 4/5 watched a movie 6/7 typed 8 lunch 9/10 took notes did a w/s 11 took notes and did a w/s....this morning i was walking with kris and jamie...we were lookin for bush and sure enough we came around the corner and there he was...i was so happy to see him..lols. then he had to go so i went to h/r. after school was out he waited for me outside then we walked to his bus then came home...mom is still kinda sick...awww..then got on here to look for pics for art...but it doesn't look like i am..lols...well that is about it for now update later gnat...
luv ya bush

today i went over bush's at say about 1:30....because my momo said that i didn't have to go to my cousin's candle party.lol then i came home and now i am here waiting for him to call. for valentines day he got me a teddy bear and a necklace and chocolate...what a sweetie! luv him so much! well that is about all for now nothing really happens to me so i iwll update later byes....gnat

today we had a 2 hour delay AGAIN which is great because i haven't had english for like 5 dayz....yeah! sat. i went to nemacolin's new huntin store, the movies, and out to eat all with bush..i was really happy since i don't get to see him that often ne more so that was really good..i missed him do much! then sun. i went to church then bush came here for a while..then i watched the game! that was stinkin pathetic...i swear i was mad..errr....but o well what can you do...? at least i got to see bush! well that is about all..i will update later...love ya bush.....and my bugg and buggettes...lols..
~*~raye - i gotta handful right?? lol
peace out..GnAt

ok guys...today was the day we switched classes because of 2nd semester...art is fun..typing will be just"lovely" (said sarcastically) and yes bush went to tech and i was very sad! today after 3rd. i found myself waiting for him thinking he was still there...then the rest of the day i kept feeling like he was just sick and comin back tomorrow..but i know it isn't true...i wish...but it isn't! *cries* i just hope he has a good time and learns what he has to learn. lol....well that is about all for now..update laters..peace...pontie python! (hehe raye thanks for the name by the way)

today the steelers play in Tenn. and i hope we win!! GO STEELERS! bush is comin over to watch the game with me! yea...and guess what...today is our one month anniversary! yeahs....i am soo happy....well he should be comin in a bit...i better go update laterz...peace....gNAT

bush and i have been together for 24 dayz...yea! i am soo happy! he is such a nice guy! lol...today i went shoppin and i got a cord skirt..and then we went to k-mart and got a new phone...tomorrow i have to go to church and then i am either goin to bush's or he is comin here dunno yet...lols well that is about all for now update later..peace...nush

bush and i have been together for 24 dayz...yea! i am soo happy! he is such a nice guy! lol...today i went shoppin and i got a cord skirt..and then we went to k-mart and got a new phone...tomorrow i have to go to church and then i am either goin to bush's or he is comin here dunno yet...lols well that is about all for now update later..peace...nush

me and gummie bear have been together for 15 dayz! awwww....i am at raye's crib now....love her gift she got me..x-mas was fun...bush liked his gift...his hat looks good on him...i am still waiting for my gift...i am goin over his crib tomorrow..lols..well gots to be goin...update laterz..peace ; )
~gnat~

christmas is comin soon guys...i can't wait...i hope bush likes what i got him! lols...school today was fun...because we didn't do anything...got my nails done with kris..they look nice. prolly go to the mall tomorrow AGAIN!! lols..everything is peachy..couldn't be better....that is about all i will update later peace....bugg
luv ya bush!

Happy Birthday To Me...today was ok...had a 2 hour delay..got to school and raye, jamie, and bee weren't there. and i didn't think that bush was there either and i was upset. but after first we just went to 4/5 because of the delay...and after 4/5 cherie was like theres your b-friend and i said what and i turned around and there he was! YEA! then he came up behind me and said happy birthday and hugged me. well lunch wasn't to bad...then the walk to biology...brittany dillow said that he was goin ask me out but he was scared and he would be late for class so he said i will next time i see her...which he did on the way to my math class...i was sooo happy i ran to kristy!!! and then she started to scream! all of my friends are so happy that i have found someone and so am i! lols well that is about all for now....update later...peace....bugg

i can't wait...there are only 2 dayz and i will be 15!! yeas!! well to get on with life..today was cool..i guess. bush is sooo nice..i am really glad we met! and i mean that! i am so lucky to have him....and shh don't tell but i am thinkin about sayin.....yes...soon! don't tell....(even tho he will prolly see this) but he is just such a nice guy and there are just no words that can explain how i feel! lol.....but i am sure you all see us in the hallway together and you know what i mean...hehe...but i just wanted to update my life here and i will be back sometime soon...peace...bugg

ok...i know i haven't updated in a WHILE! but hey what can i say i'm a busy gal! lols..well school is good...thanksgiving was great my sister came home for the week to be with us! and my b-day is in 4 dayz just 4 dayz! i can't wait..lol...but guess what??...the boy i have been crushin on for awhile likes me!! yea!!! we told each other about our feelings...i am soo happy! he is the best thing to happen since oct. 6th! lols...he is sooo sweet..and he actually listens to me when i talk.. plus he is my height!! YES! i was so happy all week..you can ask my friends....i couldn't take my smile off my face....: ) i was ecstatic! i just hope when we go together that everything is great...and not terrible which, in my opinion, it will be more than great!! lols! well that is about all for now...i will try and update more than i have been...peace.....bugg

today we didn't have ne school so raye spent the night last night...and i know i haven't updated in a long time but o well!..there has been alot on my mind! i took my nails off....boy did that hurt! lols! but i will get them back for christmas! tomorrow is my 1 month anniversary of being single! i don't know whether to be happy or sad! confused! well.. that is about all for now NITE
pontie

soooo much stuff has been goin on for the past i dunno how many dayz! and everyone i am sure knows about me and zac about now!! errr..well ne ways school as been a killer...i tell ya...dancin is fun...and it has been cold!! um..today i went with raye to the octoberfest...myan was HOT!!.....we were froze!!!....then came back to rayes house! we are dancin our a**es off!...we aren't too happy right now! we just don't seem to find the RIGHT guy ever if we think we do they end up breaking our hearts and go for some other girl then they lie to us about it!!! errrrrrrrr..."boys are smelly..throw rocks at them"......hahahahahaha i crack myself up!!well that is about all for now wrtie LATER peace nat
"the only boy worth your tears is the one that doesn't make you cry"

today went with kris and raye to get my nails done then saw a movie which was great..only i wish i had a guy there with me.....then went to bon-ton and hit my head ~ouch~...then took kris home and raye went home then i went out to eat...that is all today....zac and i are finally talkin now....i miss him soo much! i think he is happier and better off without me....don't you think....? i dunno well i gtg byes
nat

i really liked zac...i don't think he knows how much i liked him!! i tell ya out of the blue he just says i don't want a g/f ne more...what is up with that! i just need some time for this to sink in! i don't understand! i wish i did....well i will be back later maybe peace
natalie
FRIDAY IS GOIN BE 4 MONTHS FOR ME AND ZAC!!! I LUV YA HUNNY! *MUAH* (and a million more times)

i know i haven't updated in a while but i just never got around to it! well all week was spirit week and friday was the best because raye and i made shirts for the pep rally they were (as zac would say) bitchin! then homecoming was suppose to friday but due to the large amount of rain is was set to be sat. well i went and zac was there and him and kayla were fightin ( i can't stand that ) *cries* it was freezing sat. but zac is standin there in shorts and a hoodie and i am in a hoodie and jeans he is hot and i am freezin! what is up wit that!? well he kept me warm...then today i went to church and parker and colby were there...um...that is all with church when i got home i saw zac had called so i tried to call him back and there was no answer so i called about 6 moer times today and no one was home! i tell ya! i wonder what he wanted..? i hope he calls when he gets home! well that is about it and i will try and update later peace nat

today...parker got baptized in church and colby was there too...then went home and went to the mall got my nails done they look good! then went to wal*mart and i got the tights raye....then came home took a nap then ate dinner..then went to my aunt's came home called zac and talked for a while then got off! love him muchly! alot----alot----alot!!! then got on here! talkin to raye....tomorrow is mix-n-match day! i am not really mixin and matchin i am just...y'all see tomorrow! lols....well that is about it! update later peace..nat

nothing much happened.....it was really hot in school today..um..my biology test was really HARD!! i wish i would have studied more!! errrr.....then came home and called zac because i had dancin tonite..which in fact was fun...this was the first time that sweat actually ran down my face! eewwww...but then came home and called jamie and zac talked for a bit...and yes zac i am sorry still! lols luv ya....ya wanna know something he is the greatest because his phone died and he called beack sayin " i don't have much time so luv you bye...."laugh laugh" luv you bye..bye..." isn't he the greatest and sweetest...i just don't know what i would do if we broke up! i would be heartbroken!! i don't even wanna think about breakin up! but i have to go now...i will update later...peace natalie   ~*~luv ya zac~*~

nothing really happened to.....zac looked pretty good today...wait he looks good everyday...lols.....at lunch raye almost got me with ketchup! errr...had a sub for muzina and turner....the day went fast! but i am glad it did!! can't wait til friday....it was really hot today and will be hot tomorrow!! went out to eat with my mom and dad for my mom's birthday....zac you better watch out there were these boys checkin me out! don't worrie tho you are much cuter then them!! well that is about all...update later peace nat
luv ya zac!!!

nothing really happened...but yesturday my mom and dad went ot my sister's college and she is fine....i stayed with my aunt and we went shoppin for my mom's b-day which is tomorrow! HAPPY BIRTHDAY MOM! then today woke up early! i wore a really *cute* outfit! got a lot of compliments. then..i didn't have math class we had to go to the gym...didn't get to talk with zac *cries* came home ate slept for like 3 hours....zac called twice "yeas" then called him bakc he is the best b/f i could ask for he is the best... i luv him! LUV YA ZAC!! then had to eat dinner...collected leaves for biology! then typed my essay for english....then zac called talked for a bit..he had to go then got on here....that is about it.....o and yesturday i saw colby in mickey d's i was sooo happy he is doin so well!!! go colby!!
well i will update later...peace....nat

omg!! first of all....i thought zac might be at the football game friday night well i get there and i asked aaron if he saw him and he said ya like 5 mins ago....then i asked him like durin the 2nd quarter did you see him and he said ya he is lookin for you and then i said you better not be lyin to me!!...then during the 3rd quarter i asked him again and he said ya but he told me that zac didn't want to talk to me....well towards the end of the 3rd quarter he said he was messin around with me and zac wasn't there...i was furious and i was tellin him off meanwhile when logan got there he said zac should me comin because i am takin him home.....then today..i find out that my sister is in a car wreck!! it was her and 2 other girls in the car and my sister has a bruise on her arm the other girl has a few scratches on her face and the other one is fine...but some person hit my sister on the driver's side and my sister's car is totaled!!! i am glad she isn't hurt tho.....and to top it all off...i have been tryin to get ahold of zac ALL day and then i finally get to talk to him and he said he can't talk because he has a friend over...i said well i won't get to talk to you tomorrow and he said why and i said because i will be with my aunt because me sister was in a car wreck and my parents have to go to her college and he said is she all right and i said she is fine...then he said well i have to go since i have a friend here and i said ok.....bye and he said bye and hung up........i swear my weekend is goin sooo bad......i just want to cry BIG TIME!! but there are other people out there that have it worse then me.....um...and i am really sorry aaron for flippin on you! well i will update later peace

.....the football game sucked but hangin with my friends was AWESOME!! especially raye and zac!! lols..... ale' jess and em....you guys did a good job...YAYS!! zac is a sweetheart..even tho we had a misunderstandin....we worked it out! last game was better...there weren't too many peeps there! o well maybe next one there will be...i know there will be alot at homecomin. raye spent the night....didn't stay up late...o and HAPPY B-DAY LOGAN!! even tho it was like 2 million dayz ago! lols...well that is about all..so update laters peace outie gnat

well kids.....there is just TOO much to write so i will make it short and sweet! LIFE IS GREAT! the frist week of school was ok i guess except that i only have 1 class with zac and i have lunch with raye and i did have 10th with her but she got her schedule changed (not her choice)....my schedule is..
h.r./1st...Ballas, 2nd..Halfin, 3rd...Gym errr, 4/5...Muzina, 6/7...Callahan, 8..LUNCH, 9/10..Courie, 11th...Turner....well that is about it i went to the football game fri. walked with my b/f zac the whole time...we lost 41-20 we suck!! then there is one this fri. i am goin...and a soccer game thrus. (zac logan and steve play) so come watch!! well..that is about it "FOR NOW"  update later peace ...gnat

ok...i had 2 LONG  dayz!! i will start with yesturdday/last night! well...first at like 8:30 a.m. raye called and said you up? and i said i was about to get in the tub! and she said well i am comin over now....well i got my bath and then she came we got ready for kristers to come get us. then kristers came and we went to the mall to get our nails done! after the nails thing...we went into the mall. we shopped around..in front of Value City this guy (the vj for upn 19) was signin auotgraphs and we got one..then we were eatin pizza and  raye was like "LOGAN ,LOGAN" and we chased him from rosa pizza to k.b. toys and he finally turned around he smiled and then just kept walkin he totally blew us off! errrr..o well!! then kris dropped me and raye off at my house...then raye's mom came and got us to go to her house.....we picked kristy up and we saw RYAN FEARS.....RAYE WAS ECSTACTIC!!!!  we came to raye's and got ready for the dance! we looked pretty good! then we were off...on our way we saw travis (zac's bro)he was drivin!! WOW! then we got there and we saw ryan and his crew and i introduced me and raye..then i saw zac and we were hangin out! we all started dancin and i was dancin all up on zac! (i know it prolly wasn't too good but i just wanted to get close to him) lols! RYAE AND RYAN SLOW DANCED!!then zac and i slowed danced together aww...i kissed him like 2 times!! YEA!!! then when we were leavin his mom said you ready to go zac and he was like ya and kristy was like what about the kiss and i pulled him back and his mom turned around and we couldn't....then i found out that zac's mom said you could have kissed her i wouldn't have cared!! I LOVE HER SHE IS SOO COOL!! then...justin (raye's bro) was comin home this weekend and rayes dad picked us up and said justin said he wanted to stay another day at college...when we got to rayes the lights were on and kris walks in and screams JUSTIN!!! so mr.cerullo lied to us! o well! then we got online and were talkin to zac and ryan fears..that was fun! kris and i spent the night..then this morning me and kris went with raye and her mom and aunt pat to teh mall...raye and her aunt pat got their nails done! how pretty!! we walked through the mall a bit and then went out to eat! ITALIAN OVEN..YUMMIE! thanks raye! after that we went to wal*mart....*SNORT...LAH DEE DAH....HEEE....LOLY LOLY LOL!!! hahahaha! funnny!! well we left wal*mart and we took kristy home and then i went to rayes because i forgot my camera..then they brought me home....we called zac..talked for a bit...then raye left..called zac back but he had to go because his aunt and uncle came!....then did nothing i wanted to go get my pics. developed (1 hour) but my mom said it wasn't that important...errrr. i want those pics!!! o well...school starts monday..noooooo...at least i get to see my friends and my *HUNNY* *ZAC* awww...well that is about all for now update later peace
GnAt

nothing really happened today..raye didn't come over because she wasn't feelin well...so she is comin in the morning and then we are off to the mall with kristy!! GETTIN MY NAILS DONE!! i went and looked at the names for the highschool and i am in ballas..i have a few peoples but not tooo many! not raye kris or zac!! *cries* then i went to k*mart and saw travis embacher! and came home called zac and he sounds alittle bit sick (cough cough)....found out that he might not make it to the dance because of soccer pics...he doesn't want them tho..so..and he said he can get his uniform another time!! awww how sweet!! well that is about all! update later! peace gnat

today...first my sister and mom went to the mall to get their new cell phones...i stayed home..called raye and zac wasn't home...then when mom came home.....we ate lunch...then went swimming....she also signed me up for dancing....then my aunt came and went swimming...after she left we ate dinner then me and my sister went bowling with my aunt, uncle, cousin, and others.....came home called zac to see how his scrimmage went...(went well).....then got off the phone with him called raye and talked forever....then made a bracelet and now i am here...well that is about all..i will update later....peace gnat!

i was really happy today because my mom said that zac could come over today and spend the day with me!!YEA!! we sat in the house for a bit and everything and of course WE KISSED!! so happy....then we just talked and stuff! he is the coolest boyfriend i have ever had!!seriously!! i can actually talk to him and stuff!! lols! then i went to wal*mart and then to my aunt's i got my hair cut!! a little bit below my chin!!WOW!!
then came home and called raye......i will have to call zac and wish him luck for his soccer scrimmage! GOOD LUCK ZAC!! well update later peace....gnat

today was basically the same as ne other..but we went SHOPPIN today. i got some jeans and shirts and stuff like that. i also found out that raye gets to spend the night thrusday night then friday kris is pickin us up and we are gettin our nails done while raye sits there and then we are shoppin..after that kris is droppin us off at my house then raye's mom is pickin us up later in the day..we are pickin kris up and then gettin ready for the DANCE!! can't wait..i hope zac comes to the dance because....ya know.....our first slow dance...aww! alittle nervous...never really "danced" with a boy that has ment this much to me...all the others i was pushed to dance with! so....excited/nervous! lols i will be fine! but i will update later byes! peace gnat

i mess everything up...no matter what it is i mess it up....zac is such a great person and i can't tell him ne thing (nothing to do with breakin up) i just wish i could open up more...i think my problem is that i am afraid to let ne one in because i might get hurt! well i know zac wouldn't hurt me..but i am "a keep to myself" kinda person.....i hope i can talk to him better...SOON! i love you zac! i will always love you no matter what! well i will update later..peace

i mess everything up...no matter what it is i mess it up....zac is such a great person and i can't tell him ne thing (nothing to do with breakin up) i just wish i could open up more...i think my problem is that i am afraid to let ne one because i might get hurt! well i know zac wouldn't hurt me..but i am "a keep to myself" kinda person.....i hope i can talk to him better...SOON! i love you zac! i will always love you no matter what! well i will update later..peace

i talked to zac today..again....aren't you happy for us?! hahaha lols! ne ways this dance at pal's club...i might go..i hope zac can go because i want to slow dance with him...lols....how romantic!! hahahaha (to trll ya the truth this is the 1st b/f that I WANTED to slow dance with..the rest my friends pushed me to dance with...even tho i am not very good!) lols!i hope we both can go..hopefully he isn't too tired from soccer! well......i am goin school clothes shoppin either sat. or mon.! how excitin! justin (raye's bro) leaves for college tomorrow! you are goin love bein an only child raye..believe me! well i gtg call raye byes update later! peace
GnAt or as zac's bro now says BUG!  what a......nevermind!

there is just so much i want to write right now....it is crazy! i am just in a terrible mess!! no one can understand it...i am just too upset to talk about it!..i want to...but i just don't have the words.....blah is basically all!!so i will try and find the words and i will update later peace natalie

today...we went to wal-mart and shoppin save! we also rented a walk to remember! it is soo good i cried! then i called zac and i found out that he hurt his knee (kinda) skateboardin he said it isn't serious but he didn't play soccer yesturday because it was hurtin...i asked him why he didn't tell me and he said well it isn't that serious!! i wish i would have told me sooner! and i feel like we are fadin apart! *cries* we never talk ne more and .....it upsets me!! well now i am here...i will update later! peace nat

MY SISTER CAME HOME FROM MAINE TODAY! my mom was so worried because she was delayed on the plane because of a storm...and after alot of waiting she finally arrived!! then we were goin go out to eat but when we got there...i accidently shut my dad's fingers in the door!! OUCH! i felt soooooo bad! then we got wendy's instead! when we came home we went to k-mart and then to my aunt's house!!came home and then....watched lord of the rings and now i am here! well update later peace gnat

TODAY WAS THE PEACH FEST AT MY CHURCH!! FUN FUN FUN!! emily n. and i called zac to see if he wanted to come to the peach fest and he couldn't because logan was there and they were goin to a concert! DARN! o well...then emily invited me to go with her to the regatta in pittsburgh! and i was allowed! (her family has boats and they all were there) it was sooo much fun! you should have seen the fireworks! they were BEAUTIFUL!! i just wish zac was there!! *cries* i stayed on the boat with them and her mom was tempted to take us home because the boat next to us got a little OUT OF CONTROL!! then on sunday we went to watch the boat races and they were awesome! thenher mom drove home while me em and her dad drove the boat (on the water) from pittsburgh to brownsville! WOW we waited 3 HOURS for the last lock we were goin through but finally we made it through and we made it to one of the docks and we ate dinner em's mom met us their then they brought me home around 11:30 and that is about it! so i will update later! peace gnat

well.....today was soo boring...you won't believe it! i never talked to zac! *cries* i think logan was there ne ways...why would he want to talk to me!!?? i can't talk to him tomorrow because my church is havin a peach fest and i will be there ALL day!but that is about all.....i hope i get to see him soon i can't take the suspence!! (my life sounds like a soap opera) lols well...i will update tomorrow, if i'm not to tired from the peach fest! well...peace....gnat

well.....today was sooo borin!! i barely talked to zac and then he told me tonight that he had to cut off the necklace that i got him when he broke his hip (a hemp necklace) because of soccer practice/conditioning...i am happy he gets to play...well then i talked to him alittle bit ago and he left me to go run! :*( o well... then i started to stretch..because i am startin dancin again this year and i need to stretch bad!! i mean bad!! then i watched some old dance tapes..boy i sucked!!! i prolly still do!! lols then i got on here that is about all! so i will update again later! peace GnAt

the reason why i say zac is awesome is because...i was talkin to him on the phone and his phone was dyin and it hung up on me and then like 2-3 mins. later he calls and says, "I just called to say bye, bye i love you" isn't that soo sweet! he is *SWEETIE PIE*( even tho we always say i love you to each other! ) well.....today was my aunt's b-day! HAPPY BIRTHDAY!! i went to her house for pizza and cake then came home talked to jamie and then *ZAC* that is about all tho! so i will update l8terz!! peace!
gNaT..a.k.a..SwEeT tHaNg

i talked to zac for like 3hours tonite!!i am soo happy! he is the best b/f ne one could ask for!! and i told him that when i was at my aunt's i was showin her where he went on vaca. and later i showed my mom and i said he wants me to go to the beach with him and i just said in 2 years and they said well you will be in....11th grade so ya you could prolly go it you 2 were still goin out!! i was totally surprised!! i was soo happy! LOVE YA ZAC!! well today  i went to my aunt's house for the day because she hasn't been feelin well so i went ot help her wash clothes and stuffs then i ate dinner and my mom came and got me...called jamie and raye then called zac and talked for like i said 3 hours!! WOW!! well that is about all i will update later! peace GnAt

today i went to raye's house for a few hours...we swam then it rained on us then we went back to her house (because the pool is at her mama's)we ate and watched a MOVIE! (center stage)then just hung around...justin's g/f megan came over....then they left....then my mom came and i left....came home and called zac we only talked for like 20 mins....his phone was goin dead!! *cries* but he said he would call me tomorrow! yea! that is about it! so i am goin go peace gNaT
